Lecture 16: Git Revert, Tags, GitHub Clone, GitLab
Git Revert
git revert
Roman Urdu:
Revert safe hai kyun ke new commit banata hai, history change nahi karta.
Git Tags
git tag v1.0
git tag -d v1.0
Roman Urdu:
Tags releases mark karne ke liye use hotay hain.
Git Clone
git clone
Roman Urdu:
Clone remote repository ko local system pe copy karta hai.
Git Revert vs Reset
Feature — Revert — Reset
Safe for sharing — Yes — No
History change — No — Yes
Use case — Production — Local
Roman Urdu:
Interview rule: Reset local ke liye, Revert production ke liye
Additional Git Commands
git log
Roman Urdu:
Ye commands debugging aur history check karne ke liye use hoti hain.
